    contacts_n INT,
    contacts_n_1 INT,
    contacts_n_2 INT,
    contacts_n_3 INT,
    contacts_n_4 INT,
    contacts_n_5 INT,
    contacts_n_6 INT,
    contacts_n_7 INT,

    new_market VARCHAR
